name: Crawler Dendrite
desc:
FLIP: You can send 1 monster from your Deck to the GY.
If this face-up card in its owner's control leaves the field because of an opponent's card effect: You can Special Summon 2 "Crawler" monsters with different names from your Deck in face-down Defense Position, except "Crawler Dendrite" and "Acid Crawler". You can only use each effect of "Crawler Dendrite" once per turn.
